# Repo Structure (Astro Showcase)

## Expected Layout
- `src/pages/` for routes
- `src/components/` for reusable UI
- `src/layouts/` for shared page frames
- `src/content/` for case-study markdown/content collections
- `public/` for static assets
- `docs/` for supporting technical notes

## Content Conventions
- One case study per page or markdown file.
- Use predictable slugs and titles.
- Keep diagrams and screenshots in organised asset folders.